controller

Class FileController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.Controller
      • controller.FileController

  • public class FileController
extends Controller
    Controller class for opening conference files and parsing them. This class is used for gathering the conference data and allowing for easy data gathering.
    Version:
    6/3/2014
    Author:
    Nick Ames, Richard Hemingway, Tim Loverin, Yeonil Yoo
